ma b´aj.' N-chi b´et ky-b´et twitz t-xe t-xaq t-xaq b´e. Atzaj te' kyjatz, tzaj tq'o'n mar
n-chi tzaj t-xo´n tib´aj cubierta, tib´aj ky-bomba te qonik´an extzen tzmax ky-qan. E jaw ẍchʼin kyibʼaj
