A Jack Thayer extzen a Milton Long n-chi yolin kyi´j qa n-chi b´et ky-xo´n. A davit n-chi ajb´en kye te jun tajlal
tzaj tyek´un a Titanic n-chi b´et mas jurat jalin. Thayer tajtoq tu´n t-xi´ t-xo´n tib´, tu´n t-xi ttzyu´n jun t-xmilal
a bark te kolb´il n-ku tz´aq, n-ku tz´aq extzen n-ok t-xo´n tib´ kyi´j bark n-ku tz´ok tka´yin 500 mo 600 yardas najchaq.
jun tb´anil b´etb´il. Long, mya b´a´n, n-chi yolin ti´j extzen n-chi yolin ti´j Thayer mya
tun t-xi t-ximana.
