Noqtzun tu´nj, junjun lajoj xjal b´ant ky-ten ky-nab´l ex ky-ipumal. Kye qe jlu, kab´e q´uqb´il kyk´u´j
aju kolbʼil in tzaj toj aʼ bʼaj t-sbʼuʼn tibʼ – aʼyeju in che bʼaj t-xiten A ex B. Kykabʼil otoq che kubʼ tzʼaq tiʼj bark in kubʼ tzʼaq
cubierta, A pantano ex B t-xe. Extzun aju embudo n-ku tz´aq n-chi tx´jet kykab´il bark mas t-xilen
kye xjal. Jalin aye nadadores mas kyipumal extzen mas at ky-suerte n-chi ok kymojb´a´n kyib´aj.
Tej tik´ junlo kab´laj minut, a Olaus Abelseth n-chi tzaj t-xo´n tib´ ttxlaj A. B´a´n t-xilen junlajtl
ya otoq tz´okx tmij kyimni toj bark n-chi b´et. Mintiʼ e onin ex mintiʼ e ok ten qʼamalte te ik tzeʼn te
n-chi b´et tib´aj gunwale. Noq o´kx n-chi kyq´ama´n, 'Mi´n tz´ok t-xo´na bark.'
