up sagging spirits.
Atxix toj amb´il lu n-chi ky-ka´yin twitz tx´otx´ n-chi jyon kyi´j junjun techlal. At junjun amb´il n-chi b´et
n-chi tzalaj kyi´j ky-q´ob´ q´ankyaq n-chi q´aq´in tu´n Boxhall toj bark 2. Axpe ikx te Lightoller kub´ t-ximin qa il ti´j tu´n ky-pon
te juntl bark.
