extzen aye xjal n-chi el kypa´n kyib´ kyi´j mya b´a´n tu´n ky-ka´yin mas nya b´a´n – Miss Sue Eva
A Rule n-ok tq´o´n twitz ti´j jun xu´j noq jun toalla turca tok ti´j t-xu´k extzen jun tb´anil t-xmakal
t-xb´alun te qonik´an tib´aj t-xu´k. Aye t-xb´alin jun t-xaq t-xb´alin te qonik´an b´incha´n tuk´il t-xb´alin
t-xb´alun ... kimonos ... abrigos de pelo ... chales de lana llana ... pijamas ... botas de goma ... saq
zapatillas de satén. Extzun atzun jun amb´il te t-xilen t-xnaq´tzb´il – jun tajlal b´isb´ajil kye xu´j n-chi ky-b´inchen
sombreros extzen aye xinaq snap-brim tweed gorras.
Aju´ mas b´isb´ajil kyxol kykyaqil aju´ ch´in yol. Ch´ixmi mya jun yol tzaj q´ma´n. Kykyaqil xjal n-chi ky-ka´yin; tyaqilx
at junxitl t-xilen. A Reverendo PMA Hoques, jun xjal n-chi b´et toj Carpathia,
n-ximana qa aye xjal n-chi tzaj ky-xob´il tun ky-yolin. A capitán Rostron kub´ t-ximin qa kykyaqil xjal noq
nimxix aq´untl. A Lawrence Beesley kub´ tna´n qa mya nimxix ky-xob´il extzen mya nimxix ky-aq´un - noq o´kx ky-b´et
twitz jun tiy nimxix t-xilen tun t-xi q-tzyu´n.
